    "Jos 14:1": "And these are the countries which the children H1121 of Israel inherited in the land of Canaan, which Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son H1121 of Nun, and the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children H1121 of Israel, distributed for inheritance to them.",
