    "Jos 14:6": "Then the children H1121 of Judah came unto Joshua in Gilgal: and Caleb the son H1121 of Jephunneh the Kenezite said unto him, Thou knowest the thing that the LORD said unto Moses the man of God concerning me and thee in Kadeshbarnea.",
