    "Jos 15:12": "And the west border was to the great sea, and the coast thereof. This is the coast of the children H1121 of Judah round about according to their families.",
    "Jos 15:13": "And unto Caleb the son H1121 of Jephunneh he gave a part among the children H1121 of Judah, according to the commandment of the LORD to Joshua, even the city of Arba the father of Anak, which city is Hebron.",
