    "Jos 17:3": "But Zelophehad, the son H1121 of Hepher, the son H1121 of Gilead, the son H1121 of Machir, the son H1121 of Manasseh, had no sons, H1121 but daughters: and these are the names of his daughters, Mahlah, and Noah, Hoglah, Milcah, and Tirzah.",
    "Jos 17:4": "And they came near before Eleazar the priest, and before Joshua the son H1121 of Nun, and before the princes, saying, The LORD commanded Moses to give us an inheritance among our brethren. Therefore according to the commandment of the LORD he gave them an inheritance among the brethren of their father.",
