    "Jos 18:14": "And the border was drawn thence, and compassed the corner of the sea southward, from the hill that lieth before Bethhoron southward; and the goings out thereof were at Kirjathbaal, which is Kirjathjearim, a city of the children H1121 of Judah: this was the west quarter.",
    "Jos 18:16": "And the border came down to the end of the mountain that lieth before the valley of the son H1121 of Hinnom, and which is in the valley of the giants on the north, and descended to the valley of Hinnom, to the side of Jebusi on the south, and descended to Enrogel,",
    "Jos 18:17": "And was drawn from the north, and went forth to Enshemesh, and went forth toward Geliloth, which is over against the going up of Adummim, and descended to the stone of Bohan the son H1121 of Reuben,",
    "Jos 18:20": "And Jordan was the border of it on the east side. This was the inheritance of the children H1121 of Benjamin, by the coasts thereof round about, according to their families.",
