    "Jos 18:28": "And Zelah, Eleph, and Jebusi, which is Jerusalem, Gibeath, and Kirjath; fourteen cities with their villages. This is the inheritance of the children H1121 of Benjamin according to their families.",
    "Jos 19:1": "And the second lot came forth to Simeon, even for the tribe of the children H1121 of Simeon according to their families: and their inheritance was within the inheritance of the children H1121 of Judah.",
