    "Jos 19:40": "And the seventh lot came out for the tribe of the children H1121 of Dan according to their families.",
    "Jos 19:47": "And the coast of the children H1121 of Dan went out too little for them: therefore the children H1121 of Dan went up to fight against Leshem, and took it, and smote it with the edge of the sword, and possessed it, and dwelt therein, and called Leshem, Dan, after the name of Dan their father.",
