    "Jos 19:49": "When they had made an end of dividing the land for inheritance by their coasts, the children H1121 of Israel gave an inheritance to Joshua the son H1121 of Nun among them:",
    "Jos 19:51": "These are the inheritances, which Eleazar the priest, and Joshua the son H1121 of Nun, and the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children H1121 of Israel, divided for an inheritance by lot in Shiloh before the LORD, at the door of the tabernacle of the congregation. So they made an end of dividing the country.",
    "Jos 20:2": "Speak to the children H1121 of Israel, saying, Appoint out for you cities of refuge, whereof I spake unto you by the hand of Moses:",
    "Jos 20:9": "These were the cities appointed for all the children H1121 of Israel, and for the stranger that sojourneth among them, that whosoever killeth any person at unawares might flee thither, and not die by the hand of the avenger of blood, until he stood before the congregation.",
    "Jos 21:1": "Then came near the heads of the fathers of the Levites unto Eleazar the priest, and unto Joshua the son H1121 of Nun, and unto the heads of the fathers of the tribes of the children H1121 of Israel;",
