    "Jos 22:20": "Did not Achan the son H1121 of Zerah commit a trespass in the accursed thing, and wrath fell on all the congregation of Israel? and that man perished not alone in his iniquity.",
    "Jos 22:21": "Then the children H1121 of Reuben and the children H1121 of Gad and the half tribe of Manasseh answered, and said unto the heads of the thousands of Israel,",
    "Jos 22:24": "And if we have not rather done it for fear of this thing, saying, In time to come your children H1121 might speak unto our children, H1121 saying, What have ye to do with the LORD God of Israel?",
