    "Jos 22:31": "And Phinehas the son H1121 of Eleazar the priest said unto the children H1121 of Reuben, and to the children H1121 of Gad, and to the children H1121 of Manasseh, This day we perceive that the LORD is among us, because ye have not committed this trespass against the LORD: now ye have delivered the children H1121 of Israel out of the hand of the LORD.",
