    "Jdg 6:11": "And there came an angel of the LORD, and sat under an oak which was in Ophrah, that pertained unto Joash the Abiezrite: and his son H1121 Gideon threshed wheat by the winepress, to hide it from the Midianites.",
    "Jdg 6:29": "And they said one to another, Who hath done this thing? And when they enquired and asked, they said, Gideon the son H1121 of Joash hath done this thing.",
