    "Jdg 7:14": "And his fellow answered and said, This is nothing else save the sword of Gideon the son H1121 of Joash, a man of Israel: for into his hand hath God delivered Midian, and all the host.",
    "Jdg 8:10": "Now Zebah and Zalmunna were in Karkor, and their hosts with them, about fifteen thousand men, all that were left of all the hosts of the children H1121 of the east: for there fell an hundred and twenty thousand men that drew sword.",
    "Jdg 8:13": "And Gideon the son H1121 of Joash returned from battle before the sun was up,",
