    "Jdg 8:28": "Thus was Midian subdued before the children H1121 of Israel, so that they lifted up their heads no more. And the country was in quietness forty years in the days of Gideon.",
    "Jdg 8:29": "And Jerubbaal the son H1121 of Joash went and dwelt in his own house.",
