    "Jdg 9:1": "And Abimelech the son H1121 of Jerubbaal went to Shechem unto his mother's brethren, and communed with them, and with all the family of the house of his mother's father, saying,",
    "Jdg 9:2": "Speak, I pray you, in the ears of all the men of Shechem, Whether is better for you, either that all the sons H1121 of Jerubbaal, which are threescore and ten persons, reign over you, or that one reign over you? remember also that I am your bone and your flesh.",
    "Jdg 9:5": "And he went unto his father's house at Ophrah, and slew his brethren the sons H1121 of Jerubbaal, being threescore and ten persons, upon one stone: notwithstanding yet Jotham the youngest son H1121 of Jerubbaal was left; for he hid himself.",
    "Jdg 9:18": "And ye are risen up against my father's house this day, and have slain his sons, H1121 threescore and ten persons, upon one stone, and have made Abimelech, the son H1121 of his maidservant, king over the men of Shechem, because he is your brother;)",
    "Jdg 9:24": "That the cruelty done to the threescore and ten sons H1121 of Jerubbaal might come, and their blood be laid upon Abimelech their brother, which slew them; and upon the men of Shechem, which aided him in the killing of his brethren.",
    "Jdg 9:26": "And Gaal the son H1121 of Ebed came with his brethren, and went over to Shechem: and the men of Shechem put their confidence in him.",
