    "Jdg 9:31": "And he sent messengers unto Abimelech privily, saying, Behold, Gaal the son H1121 of Ebed and his brethren be come to Shechem; and, behold, they fortify the city against thee.",
    "Jdg 9:35": "And Gaal the son H1121 of Ebed went out, and stood in the entering of the gate of the city: and Abimelech rose up, and the people that were with him, from lying in wait.",
    "Jdg 9:57": "And all the evil of the men of Shechem did God render upon their heads: and upon them came the curse of Jotham the son H1121 of Jerubbaal.",
    "Jdg 10:1": "And after Abimelech there arose to defend Israel Tola the son H1121 of Puah, the son H1121 of Dodo, a man of Issachar; and he dwelt in Shamir in mount Ephraim.",
    "Jdg 10:4": "And he had thirty sons H1121 that rode on thirty ass colts, and they had thirty cities, which are called Havothjair unto this day, which are in the land of Gilead.",
    "Jdg 10:6": "And the children H1121 of Israel did evil again in the sight of the LORD, and served Baalim, and Ashtaroth, and the gods of Syria, and the gods of Zidon, and the gods of Moab, and the gods of the children H1121 of Ammon, and the gods of the Philistines, and forsook the LORD, and served not him.",
    "Jdg 10:7": "And the anger of the LORD was hot against Israel, and he sold them into the hands of the Philistines, and into the hands of the children H1121 of Ammon.",
    "Jdg 10:8": "And that year they vexed and oppressed the children H1121 of Israel: eighteen years, all the children H1121 of Israel that were on the other side Jordan in the land of the Amorites, which is in Gilead.",
    "Jdg 10:9": "Moreover the children H1121 of Ammon passed over Jordan to fight also against Judah, and against Benjamin, and against the house of Ephraim; so that Israel was sore distressed.",
    "Jdg 10:10": "And the children H1121 of Israel cried unto the LORD, saying, We have sinned against thee, both because we have forsaken our God, and also served Baalim.",
