    "1Sa 9:1": "Now there was a man of Benjamin, whose name was Kish, the son H1121 of Abiel, the son H1121 of Zeror, the son H1121 of Bechorath, the son H1121 of Aphiah, a Benjamite, a mighty man of power.",
