    "1Ch 1:9": "And the sons H1121 of Cush; Seba, and Havilah, and Sabta, and Raamah, and Sabtecha. And the sons H1121 of Raamah; Sheba, and Dedan.",
    "1Ch 1:17": "The sons H1121 of Shem; Elam, and Asshur, and Arphaxad, and Lud, and Aram, and Uz, and Hul, and Gether, and Meshech.",
    "1Ch 1:19": "And unto Eber were born two sons: H1121 the name of the one was Peleg; because in his days the earth was divided: and his brother's name was Joktan.",
