    "1Ch 1:31": "Jetur, Naphish, and Kedemah. These are the sons H1121 of Ishmael.",
    "1Ch 1:32": "Now the sons H1121 of Keturah, Abraham's concubine: she bare Zimran, and Jokshan, and Medan, and Midian, and Ishbak, and Shuah. And the sons H1121 of Jokshan; Sheba, and Dedan.",
    "1Ch 1:33": "And the sons H1121 of Midian; Ephah, and Epher, and Henoch, and Abida, and Eldaah. All these are the sons H1121 of Keturah.",
    "1Ch 1:34": "And Abraham begat Isaac. The sons H1121 of Isaac; Esau and Israel.",
