    "1Ch 1:42": "The sons H1121 of Ezer; Bilhan, and Zavan, and Jakan. The sons H1121 of Dishan; Uz, and Aran.",
    "1Ch 1:43": "Now these are the kings that reigned in the land of Edom before any king reigned over the children H1121 of Israel; Bela the son H1121 of Beor: and the name of his city was Dinhabah.",
    "1Ch 1:44": "And when Bela was dead, Jobab the son H1121 of Zerah of Bozrah reigned in his stead.",
