    "1Ch 1:49": "And when Shaul was dead, Baalhanan the son H1121 of Achbor reigned in his stead.",
    "1Ch 2:1": "These are the sons H1121 of Israel; Reuben, Simeon, Levi, and Judah, Issachar, and Zebulun,",
    "1Ch 2:3": "The sons H1121 of Judah; Er, and Onan, and Shelah: which three were born unto him of the daughter of Shua the Canaanitess. And Er, the firstborn of Judah, was evil in the sight of the LORD; and he slew him.",
    "1Ch 2:4": "And Tamar his daughter in law bare him Pharez and Zerah. All the sons H1121 of Judah were five.",
