    "1Ch 2:8": "And the sons H1121 of Ethan; Azariah.",
    "1Ch 2:9": "The sons H1121 also of Hezron, that were born unto him; Jerahmeel, and Ram, and Chelubai.",
    "1Ch 2:10": "And Ram begat Amminadab; and Amminadab begat Nahshon, prince of the children H1121 of Judah;",
    "1Ch 2:16": "Whose sisters were Zeruiah, and Abigail. And the sons H1121 of Zeruiah; Abishai, and Joab, and Asahel, three.",
    "1Ch 2:18": "And Caleb the son H1121 of Hezron begat children of Azubah his wife, and of Jerioth: her sons H1121 are these; Jesher, and Shobab, and Ardon.",
    "1Ch 2:21": "And afterward Hezron went in to the daughter of Machir the father of Gilead, whom he married when he was threescore years old; H1121 and she bare him Segub.",
    "1Ch 2:23": "And he took Geshur, and Aram, with the towns of Jair, from them, with Kenath, and the towns thereof, even threescore cities. All these belonged to the sons H1121 of Machir the father of Gilead.",
    "1Ch 2:25": "And the sons H1121 of Jerahmeel the firstborn of Hezron were, Ram the firstborn, and Bunah, and Oren, and Ozem, and Ahijah.",
    "1Ch 2:27": "And the sons H1121 of Ram the firstborn of Jerahmeel were, Maaz, and Jamin, and Eker.",
    "1Ch 2:28": "And the sons H1121 of Onam were, Shammai, and Jada. And the sons H1121 of Shammai; Nadab, and Abishur.",
    "1Ch 2:30": "And the sons H1121 of Nadab; Seled, and Appaim: but Seled died without children. H1121",
    "1Ch 2:31": "And the sons H1121 of Appaim; Ishi. And the sons H1121 of Ishi; Sheshan. And the children H1121 of Sheshan; Ahlai.",
    "1Ch 2:32": "And the sons H1121 of Jada the brother of Shammai; Jether, and Jonathan: and Jether died without children. H1121",
    "1Ch 2:33": "And the sons H1121 of Jonathan; Peleth, and Zaza. These were the sons H1121 of Jerahmeel.",
    "1Ch 2:34": "Now Sheshan had no sons, H1121 but daughters. And Sheshan had a servant, an Egyptian, whose name was Jarha.",
    "1Ch 2:42": "Now the sons H1121 of Caleb the brother of Jerahmeel were, Mesha his firstborn, which was the father of Ziph; and the sons H1121 of Mareshah the father of Hebron.",
    "1Ch 2:43": "And the sons H1121 of Hebron; Korah, and Tappuah, and Rekem, and Shema.",
    "1Ch 2:45": "And the son H1121 of Shammai was Maon: and Maon was the father of Bethzur.",
    "1Ch 2:47": "And the sons H1121 of Jahdai; Regem, and Jotham, and Geshan, and Pelet, and Ephah, and Shaaph.",
    "1Ch 2:50": "These were the sons H1121 of Caleb the son H1121 of Hur, the firstborn of Ephratah; Shobal the father of Kirjathjearim,",
    "1Ch 2:52": "And Shobal the father of Kirjathjearim had sons; H1121 Haroeh, and half of the Manahethites.",
    "1Ch 2:54": "The sons H1121 of Salma; Bethlehem, and the Netophathites, Ataroth, the house of Joab, and half of the Manahethites, the Zorites.",
    "1Ch 3:1": "Now these were the sons H1121 of David, which were born unto him in Hebron; the firstborn Amnon, of Ahinoam the Jezreelitess; the second Daniel, of Abigail the Carmelitess:",
    "1Ch 3:2": "The third, Absalom the son H1121 of Maachah the daughter of Talmai king of Geshur: the fourth, Adonijah the son H1121 of Haggith:",
    "1Ch 3:9": "These were all the sons H1121 of David, beside the sons H1121 of the concubines, and Tamar their sister.",
    "1Ch 3:10": "And Solomon's son H1121 was Rehoboam, Abia his son, H1121 Asa his son, H1121 Jehoshaphat his son, H1121",
    "1Ch 3:11": "Joram his son, H1121 Ahaziah his son, H1121 Joash his son, H1121",
    "1Ch 3:12": "Amaziah his son, H1121 Azariah his son, H1121 Jotham his son, H1121",
    "1Ch 3:13": "Ahaz his son, H1121 Hezekiah his son, H1121 Manasseh his son, H1121",
    "1Ch 3:14": "Amon his son, H1121 Josiah his son. H1121",
    "1Ch 3:15": "And the sons H1121 of Josiah were, the firstborn Johanan, the second Jehoiakim, the third Zedekiah, the fourth Shallum.",
