    "1Ch 3:21": "And the sons H1121 of Hananiah; Pelatiah, and Jesaiah: the sons H1121 of Rephaiah, the sons H1121 of Arnan, the sons H1121 of Obadiah, the sons H1121 of Shechaniah.",
