    "1Ch 4:1": "The sons H1121 of Judah; Pharez, Hezron, and Carmi, and Hur, and Shobal.",
    "1Ch 4:2": "And Reaiah the son H1121 of Shobal begat Jahath; and Jahath begat Ahumai, and Lahad. These are the families of the Zorathites.",
    "1Ch 4:4": "And Penuel the father of Gedor, and Ezer the father of Hushah. These are the sons H1121 of Hur, the firstborn of Ephratah, the father of Bethlehem.",
