    "1Ch 4:27": "And Shimei had sixteen sons H1121 and six daughters; but his brethren had not many children, H1121 neither did all their family multiply, like to the children H1121 of Judah.",
    "1Ch 4:34": "And Meshobab, and Jamlech, and Joshah the son H1121 of Amaziah,",
    "1Ch 4:35": "And Joel, and Jehu the son H1121 of Josibiah, the son H1121 of Seraiah, the son H1121 of Asiel,",
