    "1Ch 7:1": "Now the sons H1121 of Issachar were, Tola, and Puah, Jashub, and Shimron, four.",
    "1Ch 7:2": "And the sons H1121 of Tola; Uzzi, and Rephaiah, and Jeriel, and Jahmai, and Jibsam, and Shemuel, heads of their father's house, to wit, of Tola: they were valiant men of might in their generations; whose number was in the days of David two and twenty thousand and six hundred.",
