    "1Ch 7:10": "The sons H1121 also of Jediael; Bilhan: and the sons H1121 of Bilhan; Jeush, and Benjamin, and Ehud, and Chenaanah, and Zethan, and Tharshish, and Ahishahar.",
    "1Ch 7:11": "All these the sons H1121 of Jediael, by the heads of their fathers, mighty men of valour, were seventeen thousand and two hundred soldiers, fit to go out for war and battle.",
