    "1Ch 7:13": "The sons H1121 of Naphtali; Jahziel, and Guni, and Jezer, and Shallum, the sons H1121 of Bilhah.",
    "1Ch 7:14": "The sons H1121 of Manasseh; Ashriel, whom she bare: (but his concubine the Aramitess bare Machir the father of Gilead:",
