    "1Ch 7:20": "And the sons H1121 of Ephraim; Shuthelah, and Bered his son, H1121 and Tahath his son, H1121 and Eladah his son, H1121 and Tahath his son, H1121",
    "1Ch 7:21": "And Zabad his son, H1121 and Shuthelah his son, H1121 and Ezer, and Elead, whom the men of Gath that were born in that land slew, because they came down to take away their cattle.",
