    "Ezr 2:42": "The children H1121 of the porters: the children H1121 of Shallum, the children H1121 of Ater, the children H1121 of Talmon, the children H1121 of Akkub, the children H1121 of Hatita, the children H1121 of Shobai, in all an hundred thirty and nine.",
    "Ezr 2:43": "The Nethinims: the children H1121 of Ziha, the children H1121 of Hasupha, the children H1121 of Tabbaoth,",
