    "Neh 6:10": "Afterward I came unto the house of Shemaiah the son H1121 of Delaiah the son H1121 of Mehetabeel, who was shut up; and he said, Let us meet together in the house of God, within the temple, and let us shut the doors of the temple: for they will come to slay thee; yea, in the night will they come to slay thee.",
