    "Neh 11:3": "Now these are the chief of the province that dwelt in Jerusalem: but in the cities of Judah dwelt every one in his possession in their cities, to wit, Israel, the priests, and the Levites, and the Nethinims, and the children H1121 of Solomon's servants.",
    "Neh 11:4": "And at Jerusalem dwelt certain of the children H1121 of Judah, and of the children H1121 of Benjamin. Of the children H1121 of Judah; Athaiah the son H1121 of Uzziah, the son H1121 of Zechariah, the son H1121 of Amariah, the son H1121 of Shephatiah, the son H1121 of Mahalaleel, of the children H1121 of Perez;",
