    "Neh 11:12": "And their brethren that did the work of the house were eight hundred twenty and two: and Adaiah the son H1121 of Jeroham, the son H1121 of Pelaliah, the son H1121 of Amzi, the son H1121 of Zechariah, the son H1121 of Pashur, the son H1121 of Malchiah,",
    "Neh 11:13": "And his brethren, chief of the fathers, two hundred forty and two: and Amashai the son H1121 of Azareel, the son H1121 of Ahasai, the son H1121 of Meshillemoth, the son H1121 of Immer,",
